<ul>
<li><span style="page:WordSection8"><span style="font-size:11pt"><span style="line-height:normal"><span style="font-family:Calibri,sans-serif"><span style="font-size:12.0pt"><span style="font-family:Palatino">If concerned for sepsis, consult EGS</span></span></span></span></span></span></li>
